highlights.text: “Babblarnas vaggvisa” by Babblarna has been on Top Songs Sweden the longest, at 1697 days straight.
Victor Leksell has the most spots on Top Songs Sweden. “Lys på mig” is the highest at #14.
“Vem edu” by Lelo and LaStreet is the highest new entry on Top Songs Sweden at #154.
“Blinka lilla stjärna där” by Adamson and Vaggvisor is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Sweden, up 96 spots at #85.
